Salesforce is the world’s leading Customer Relationship Management (CRM) platform, designed to help organizations build, manage, and grow strong customer relationships. 
Account Creation

Go to the Salesforce Developer Signup page.

Fill in your details: First Name, Last Name, Email, Role, Company, Country, and Postal Code.

Enter a unique Username in an email format (e.g., developer@yourname.com).

Agree to the terms and click Sign me up.

Check your email inbox for a verification message from Salesforce.

Click the verification link and follow the prompts to set your password and security question.
